node.text:
Dragon Capsule Crew Members recently docked successfully onto the International Space Station and here is exclusive footage tweeted by Ivan Vagner from the Expedition-63 Crew. When in such isolation in Space, it must certainly feel refreshing and joyful to unite with other astronauts.
-
#igtv #expedition #dm2 #dragoncapsule #iss #internationalspacestation #bobbehnken #doughurley #chriscassidy #nasa #spacex #commercialspace #reunited

node.text:
Dubbed 'The Hidden City', this beautiful artwork by @inwardsound depicts a bustling city encased within a tunnel like structure, with settlements in all 360° 🌃

This is of course, unrealistic (to say the least) but the image gives a great example of what a space colony might look like! The cylindrical design the artist chose for the city bears striking resemblance to that of a O’Neil Cylider, a conceptual gigantic pressurised cylinder that perpetually rotates, simulation gravity and providing a long-term habitat for potential deep space missions. Jeff Bezos is actually a big fan of O’Neil Cylinders!

Follow @orbiral for more space, science and technology content 🛸 
-
